Still glareing at the three bots in front of him Lunarpine hears 
Shadow Wings communication, "You're still functional so you're doing 
good." He replied through his comm. slowly he backs away from the 
three. He didn't want to turn his back on them but knew he had to. he 
turned , and started to run. (He's still in bot mode) As always ready 
to pull his rifle if they gave chase.

Lunarpine opened his comm once again, "I'm on my way Wing, just try 
and leave a few Preds functional for me."

trouble

> She flew off back to the Ark with her sachel full of rocks and
